    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-cared for by its previous owner. The engine is strong, the transmission shifts smoothly, and all essential electronics and safety features are fully operational. While there are some minor cosmetic imperfections and light interior wear consistent with regular use, the car is mechanically sound and provides a comfortable, reliable driving experience. It\u2019s an excellent choice for someone looking for a dependable vehicle that has plenty of life left in it.",
      "price": 33500.0,
